    "body": "This is a cool idea, but it sounds like a feature request for ganache-core - right now Ganache has no good way to do what you're asking. You could turn on time-based block production (e.g., new block every 5 seconds), but that won't be the same guarantee.\r\n\r\nFeel free to open an issue [here](https://github.com/trufflesuite/ganache-core/issues). Closing this as it does not relate to Truffle specifically. (Or @davidmurdoch / @nicholasjpaterno feel free to hit the \"transfer issue\" button if you want to just grab this one)\r\n\r\nThanks for suggesting it!",
